import React from "react";
import { MDBContainer, MDBProgress, MDBRow, MDBCol } from 'mdbreact';
import './skills.css'
const ProgressBarPage = () => {
    return (
        <section className='skills'>

        <MDBContainer>
            <MDBRow>

                <MDBCol lg="4" sm="6">
                    <MDBProgress value={0} className="my-2" />
                </MDBCol>

                <MDBCol lg="4" sm="6">
                    <MDBProgress value={25} className="my-2" />
                </MDBCol>

                <MDBCol lg="4" sm="6">
                    <MDBProgress value={50} className="my-2" />

                </MDBCol>

                <MDBCol lg="4" sm="6">
                    <MDBProgress value={75} className="my-2" />
                </MDBCol>

                <MDBCol lg="4" sm="6">
                    <MDBProgress value={100} className="my-2" />
                </MDBCol>

            </MDBRow>
        </MDBContainer>
        </section>

    );
}

export default ProgressBarPage;
